responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "50B040494349F2B89A1FAA8D1555D32C", "My current predicament is part of the evidence, yes. I had plans to inhabit a mansion in the Silver District, but Sighted presence forbids me to pursue it any further than this spot here. If I could regain my residence in the Honorsworn, I\'d be in a much better place. I advise you to turn back, and find your wits and common senses. Here, take this with you, it\'s what I have to repay you for your kindness. ")
